te-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">$ hexo deploy<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>More info: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
